(147, 1, '2012-12-18 05:56:20', '2012-12-18 05:56:20', '<span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">Sydney agency The Creative Shop and social media agency The Sound Campaign have developed an interactive out of home campaign for whiskey brand Jack Daniel''s in Japan. </span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">The execution showcases a bespoke digital photo unit known as a “High-Life Kiosk”, wherein consumers are able to place themselves into the background of three Jack Daniels ''experiences'' and take digital portraits of themselves. </span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">From being a VIP customer in a Jack Daniel''s bar, to being featured as a celebrity bill poster, all the way through to seeing their faces among bright lights as a rock''n''roll star, consumers are able to take fun images of themselves directly from the kiosk, then upload and share with friends via Facebook. </span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">David Wommelsdorff director of business development at The Creative Shop said: “This is definitely a unique experience, combining the worlds of offline with online through an integrated touch-point. We are confident that Jack Daniel’s has set the tone for innovation in the music festival environment in Japan, with many brands set to follow”. </span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">The kiosk will be featured at a series of music events throughout Japan, including but not limited to; Rock-In Japan, Rising Sun and Summersonic 2012. </span>', 'THE CREATIVE SHOP TURNS JAPANESE WITH JACK DANIEL''S', 'Sydney agency The Creative Shop and social media agency The Sound Campaign have developed an interactive out of home campaign for whiskey brand Jack Daniel''s in Japan. \r\n', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-creative-shop-turns-japanese-with-jack-daniels', '', '', '2012-12-18 06:12:08', '2012-12-18 06:12:08', '', 0, 'http://192.168.204.156/wordpress/?post_type=news&#038;p=147', 0, 'news', '', 0),
