(154, 1, '2012-12-18 06:02:42', '2012-12-18 06:02:42', '<span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">The Creative Shop has been engaged to develop a bespoke retail promotion for one of LEGO Australia''s key accounts as part of its 50th anniversary celebrations.</span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">Launching in Toys”R”Us stores nationally, ''The LEGO Super Sleuth'' promotion aims to have children recognise famous LEGO minifigures by only their silhouettes. Once the figures are identified and entered into the draw, LEGO sets are offered as weekly prizes with the major prize pool winner collecting a trip to LEGOLAND California.</span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">“Working with the LEGO brand has been a great privilege for The Creative Shop. It is a brand that is multi-generational and evokes a specific feeling and memory for almost everyone around the world. It is a brand that has done and will continue to do so much for education in all facets of the word, which no other toy brand can really match. We are proud to have been a part of this huge milestone for LEGO Australia”</span>', '50TH ANNIVERSARY OF LEGO IN AUSTRALIA - THE LEGO SUPER SLEUTH', 'The Creative Shop has been engaged to develop a bespoke retail promotion for one of LEGO Australia''s key accounts as part of its 50th anniversary celebrations.\r\n', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '50th-anniversary-of-lego-in-australia-the-lego-super-sleuth', '', '', '2012-12-18 06:11:07', '2012-12-18 06:11:07', '', 0, 'http://192.168.204.156/wordpress/?post_type=news&#038;p=154', 0, 'news', '', 0),
