4, 'http://192.168.204.156/wordpress/?p=156', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(157, 1, '2012-12-18 06:06:01', '2012-12-18 06:06:01', '<span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">The Creative Shop has joined forces with EB Games in order to bring a new and exciting digital experience to the attendees of this year''s EB Games Expo – a Digital Graffiti Wall.</span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">This innovative product is the first of its kind and allows users to explore their inner-street artist without running the risk of jail time. Using a physical spray can, people can interact as if they were creating their very own street art design. When pressed, the spray-cans emit an infrared beam that act as the cursor for users to direct and control the flow of virtual paint. Designs can be sent via email, posted to facebook, or even printed out directly for the wall itself.</span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">“This is a perfect platform for our digital graffiti wall. Electronic Boutique are the leaders in providing access to the best gaming products from around the world, which I''m certain coupled with the use of a hands-on digital graffiti wall, will be a big hit with the crowds they are sure to attract at this year''s expo”</span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">David Wommelsdorff / Director – The Creative Shop </span>', 'THE CREATIVE SHOP BRING A NEW DIGITAL EXPERIENCE TO THIS YEAR''S EB GAMES EXPO', 'The Creative Shop has joined forces with EB Games in order to bring a new and exciting digital experience to the attendees of this year''s EB Games Expo – a Digital Graffiti Wall.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-creative-shop-bring-a-new-digital-experience-to-this-years-eb-games-expo', '', '', '2012-12-18 06:10:52', '2012-12-18 06:10:52', '', 0, 'http://192.168.204.156/wordpress/?post_type=news&#038;p=157', 0, 'news', '', 0),
