(160, 1, '2012-12-18 06:07:52', '2012-12-18 06:07:52', '<span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">Tying in with Pizza Hut''s first major sporting sponsorship deal, with 2011 Formula Ford Champion and V8 Ute driver Steve Charman, The Creative Shop helped to deliver an interactive fan experience for those attending this year''s 50th anniversary of the Bathurst 1000. </span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">Promoting the NEW Pizza Hut ''PLANK'' pizza, The Creative Shop designed and developed two (2) customised interactive touch screen kiosks that allowed Bathurst 1000 fans to capture an image of themselves at the track and to relive this huge milestone for Motor Sport with family and friends via facebook. </span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">“Our photo capturing kiosks actively engage people by driving customer advocacy via an authentic and engaging brand experience. Furthermore, the virality of these moments will help Pizza Hut continue to create online interaction with their customers and build community.”</span>', 'THE CREATIVE SHOP ''PLANK'' WITH PIZZA HUT', 'Tying in with Pizza Hut''s first major sporting sponsorship deal, with 2011 Formula Ford Champion and V8 Ute driver Steve Charman, The Creative Shop helped to deliver an interactive fan experience for those attending this year''s 50th anniversary of the Bathurst 1000.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-creative-shop-plank-with-pizza-hut', '', '', '2012-12-18 06:10:36', '2012-12-18 06:10:36', '', 0, 'http://192.168.204.156/wordpress/?post_type=news&#038;p=160', 0, 'news', '', 0),
