(63, 1, '2012-12-14 03:58:40', '2012-12-14 03:58:40', 'Prior to joining TCS, David worked nationally and internationally at Real Brand &amp; Business, a company specialising in providing a turn-key offering for many fortune 500 brands across industries, including but not limited to automotive, entertainment, lifestyle, philanthropic and FMCG. During this time, David noticed an ever-growing shift toward sports based projects, such as the Doha Asian Games, Beijing Olympic Games, Guangzhou Asian Games and the Homeless World Cup, and therefore was responsible for expanding R.E.A.L''s involvement within the sporting sector through the launch of R.E.A.L Sports - a new company arm.\r\nAs VP Marketing, he was able to attract new business opportunities for the very first Youth Olympic Games, to be held in Singapore,\r\nthe Shenzhen Universiade and the London 2012 Olympic Games.\r\n\r\nCompleting both a Bachelors degree in Advertising and Marketing and an Advanced diploma in Marketing and Management, David has over 10 years experience in the advertising &amp; marketing industry and has performed for over 2 years as an industry professional teacher at TAFE NSW.\r\n\r\n"In my opinion, the need for replication of services, content and experiences across channels and seamless transitions reflects today''s consumers strong understanding of technology and their expectation for on-demand service. It is this unique relationship with technology that both represents new barriers and opportunities for today''s marketer. Similarly, marketers need to draw on a combination of good insights into customer preferences and behaviours, as well as environmental factors and sound measurement models. All designed to determine what a customer does, and indicate why they behave the way they do. Understanding the impact of every contact you have with a customer or prospect, be it direct or indirect, is the key to optimising your marketing efforts and engaging your customers."', 'Marcus Joy', 'Prior to joining TCS, David worked nationally and internationally at Real Brand & Business, a company specialising in providing a turn-key offering for many fortune 500 brands across industries, including but not limited to automotive, entertainment, lifestyle, philanthropic and FMCG', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'marcus-joy', '', '', '2012-12-14 04:03:16', '2012-12-14 04:03:16', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=director&#038;p=63', 0, 'director', '', 0),
