(144, 1, '2012-12-18 05:54:12', '2012-12-18 05:54:12', '<span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">Replacing the existing CEO; Interactive Marketing Agency The Creative Shop has appointed two Business Directors to take the company to the next level.</span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">David Wommelsdorff; Director – Business Development and Marcus Joy; Director – Project Implementation are existing employees of The Creative Shop who have been responsible for spearheading the direction of the company over the past 12 months, with the appointment following a number of recent project wins including Nokia, Bupa, Fisher &amp; Paykel, Nike, Jack Daniels – Japan, Olay and the City of Melbourne.</span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">With a focus on bridging digital with tangible in the brand activation and retail environments, The Creative Shop has been experiencing rapid growth through its continual demonstration of new and innovative interactive marketing solutions, most of which have been market firsts here in Australia.</span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">“The challenge for us is to stay ahead of the curve and to further demonstrate ourselves as market leaders for interactive marketing solutions. To this point, I am both excited and humbled by the opportunity and look forward to continuing the good work of all involved at The Creative Shop.”</span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">David Wommelsdorff </span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">Director – Business Development / The Creative Shop</span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">“Over recent times The Creative Shop has established itself as a global leader in Interactive Digital Marketing. With this in mind and with the ever changing digital landscape, our mantra is to match the insights of today with the technology of tomorrow, helping our clients go to market with unique and innovative campaigns.”</span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">Marcus Joy </span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">Director – Project Implementation / The Creative Shop</span><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><br style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #252525; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;">The Creative Shop has recently been involved in projects internationally across Japan, Korea and Kuwait, with other global markets soon to follow.</span>', 'THE CREATIVE SHOP APPOINTS TWO BUSINESS DIRECTORS', 'Replacing the existing CEO; Interactive Marketing Agency The Creative Shop has appointed two Business Directors to take the company to the next level.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-creative-shop-appoints-two-business-directors', '', '', '2012-12-18 06:12:29', '2012-12-18 06:12:29', '', 0, 'http://192.168.204.156/wordpress/?post_type=news&#038;p=144', 0, 'news', '', 0),
